  "title": "3 - 6 Months Locum Mobile Patient Service Associate PSA (Min 3 Days Per Week, OFFICE HOURS) *GOVT* #HAL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary: </strong>$13/hr (no cpf)</p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p>Mostly Office Hours that may be activated on weekdays/ weekends</p><p>Schedule will be pre-planned, might be e.g. 3 days per week or 5 days per week or no activation</p><p>(Sunday and OT pay will be provided)</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Islandwide, will follow the bus , be willing to travel across Singapore Island, depending when/where the event and the mobile bus will be.</p><p>When no events are scheduled, PSAs will be based at a Polyclinic.</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>Reporting to the Laboratory/Radiographer In-Charge, you will provide excellent customer service to patients in the Laboratory and/or Radiography sections.</p><p>• Responsible reception of patients at Diagnostics centres and/or the mobile fleets.</p><p>• Support patient service functions including registration of patients, appointment scheduling, handling of queries, billing & payment collection and general administrative tasks as assigned.</p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><p>- Min / N/ A Levels / Diploma in any field</p><p>- No experience required as training provided</p><p>-Willing to travel and work on weekends when there is a project assigned</p><p>Interested candidate, kindly send a copy of your resume to <strong>adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong><br /><br /><br /><br />Adeline Lim Xin Ying [R23112000]<br /><br />Email Address: adelinelim@recruitexpress.com.sg<br /><br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br /><br />EA Licence No: 99C4599</p>",
